            <title>Europe‚Äôs imminent winter energy crisis could have serious political consequences</title>
            <link>https://www.rt.com/russia/541863-gas-prices-rising-eu/</link>
            <guid>61a770b620302769a5058df4</guid>
            <pubDate>2021-12-01T15:42:55+00:00</pubDate>
            <author>RT</author>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[
                <!doctype html>
<html lang="en" prefix="op: http://media.facebook.com/op#">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.rt.com/russia/541863-gas-prices-rising-eu/">
